She clocks the way you carry yourself now. "Syndicate. I wondered." She doesn't stop working. "I stitch their people same as anyone's — same as Varga's. I don't ask whose coin it is, and I don't tell. You're not special, and that's the safest thing I can offer you. Try not to bleed where it shows."
* [Understood.]
    "Good. Understanding's cheap. Keeping it is the trick."
    -> END
